# Locking Script && unlocking Script

***

* Feature of script:
    * Turing incompleteness //easy to improve security
    * Stateless verification
    * Stack based language

* Example of unlocking **P2PKH**（Pay-to-Public-Key-Hash）
    * Unlocking Script:  <Sig><Pubkey>
    * Locking Script:  OP_DUP OP_HASH160 <PubkeyHash> OP_EQUALVERIFY OP_CHECKSIG
        * constitude with a pile of Stack Command and Hash
